- `J = !![kg.MODEL_OUTPUT_TOO_LONG, kg.TASK_TURN_EXCEEDED_ERROR, kg.LLM_STOP_DUP_TOOL_CALL, kg.LLM_STOP_CONTENT_LOOP, kg.DEFAULT].includes(_)` — 思考上限+循环错误标志
